  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Creation of a Community Museum for the municipality of Pisac.</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Asociaci&#xF3;n Museo Comunitario de Pisac (AMUCOP), $194,700 over two years AMUCOP will coordinate with twelve participating indigenous communities and the local municipal government to complete construction of a community museum in the District of Pisac, train community members (artisans and community staff) and begin operations.. Asociaci&#xF3;n Museo Comunitario de Pisac - AMUCOP $15,000 over six months AMUCOP will complete architectural modifications to the building that will house the community museum.</narrative>
  </description>
